Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:30.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:36.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:44.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:51.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:01:00.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:05.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:10.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:15.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:22.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,落入神秘组织 新亚特兰提斯陷阱的鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到守株待兔的空中战舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沉没于南太平洋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并未就此认输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:45.42,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#22 叛徒艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度600
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克马得海沟有多深？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,约1万公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来这点深度 根本不会构成任何影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但受损成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟能撑到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号舰队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确认多数发射声响 深水炸弹要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首左舷中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二居住区进水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰尾内壳也受损
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 于本舰正上方展开中 距离1800
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 压缩空气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,存量仅能再浮出海面一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将所有人员集合至主船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用战斗舱最后的浮力 冲撞对方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有人员请立刻至 主船舱的第2疏散室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有人员请立刻至 主船舱的第2疏散室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备分离战斗舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们待在那里不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以乱跑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的 你什么都不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚点见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至第三船舱分离完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电源转换完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前战斗舱独立运转中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自爆深度800 距离1500以上 设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切除战斗舱\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号于深度2400处 一分为二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船体被压溃成了两半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他只是将强度降低的 多余部分切除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快叫长嘴硬鳞鱼号散开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然会变成陪葬品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号已毁损 冲击波即将抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论何时 听到这声音总让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次就会轮到我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船已经没有 浮出海面的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号舰队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常抱歉 石像鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号船身解体了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 目前尚未获得确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命还真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是海底洋流 以6海浬朝西南流动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暂时就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号 深度4000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遗憾 无法继续进行追踪调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算鹦鹉螺号的船体是由 超合金宇宙钛金属构成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也无法再撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,况且它已千疮百孔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明把它逼到了墙角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却不能彻底了结它 这到底该算谁的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然无法看到 鹦鹉螺号毁灭是挺遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要向皇帝陛下报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼欧皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼有事向您报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贺喜您 尼欧皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号已经葬身于 克马得海沟下方 深度4000处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 干的好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日后为了回收 尼莫与娜蒂亚的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要借助皇帝陛下的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待属下回去之后 再向您报告详情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暂时先报告到此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 这是属下的荣幸 报告完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫与娜蒂亚都死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自一万二千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为蔚蓝之水所流的鲜血 就不曾停过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主要人员都移往辅助舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那边进行指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来啊 来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要丢啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回答我嘛 要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长室？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里不是不准任何人进入…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要将这个房间与主船舱分离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们离开这艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不具备技术的人 继续待在舰内只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我什么都愿意做 我会帮忙的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 请你保护娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船…船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人家也要啦 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不怕我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有点怕 但也有点喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 这孩子也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜 要再来陪我玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还没离开吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是手枪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早在13年前就停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从我舍弃了自己的名字 与故乡的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是从你毁灭了自己 以及我们祖国的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切都是起始于 当时的那道光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起始于杀害了 塔提苏司王国王妃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起始于杀害了 你王妃的那道光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起始于王妃遭暗杀的 塔提苏司王国政变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由叛乱者们赢得最终胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其主谋自称为『石像鬼』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并将塔提苏司王国 更名为新亚特兰提斯帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他随后拥立尼欧皇帝即位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并企图让太古时封印的 『巴别塔』重现世间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他解除了一切封印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让巴别塔恢复原来的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当石像鬼将这个破坏性武器 在众人面前展现其威力之时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悲剧发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大地笼罩在光芒之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火与风的的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,侵袭了我们整整7天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那真是一片火海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后水与地的愤怒吞噬了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仿佛是要将那座地狱 隐藏起来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原本的街道已不复在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的弟弟也因此丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经过了两天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于遇到活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个救了我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而当我明白原来那就是爱情时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己的这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我却晓得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明明不想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的打算继续 把那女孩带在身边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可是朝着地狱在前进啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在5年前就有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与石像鬼拼个你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,踏上这条沾满鲜血的不归路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我能明白你想 救更多人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你会把那个女孩带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是为了赎5年前的罪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亲手毁灭了巴别塔的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那时候也别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要停止已经启动的巴别塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯有拔除身为启动装置的 蔚蓝之水令其自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把她当成那时牺牲的 女儿的替身了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那女孩在那个地狱中 抓住了活下去的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想遵照她的希望 让她过想要的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若她有意与我们一同行动 就随她是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人生必须不断向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人不能只靠着憎恨而活是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好恨你…好想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会毁灭那座塔的理由 我不是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果没那么做 石像鬼在13年前 可能早已毁灭整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的父亲、母亲、弟弟 还有被你害死的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该都在死后的世界这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚也曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『为什么你还有脸活下去？』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直认为 你是为了要杀死石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了推翻尼欧皇帝 毁灭新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直认为你是个 为了达到此目的而不择手段的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我才会跟随你至今
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算被当成是 你女儿的替身也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能待在你身边就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到你女儿 娜蒂亚出现在你面前为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好害怕 害怕娜蒂亚会夺走你的关爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你却没有表明父亲身分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仍为了向新亚特兰提斯复仇而活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以我所深爱的男人身分 继续活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你为什么要恢复成 一名普通的父亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么不继续当那个 我深爱的男子直到最后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你 请你不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直都晓得你的恨意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓 你开枪吧\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要杀你一发子弹就够了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再问你最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为何那时你不和石像鬼 同归于尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能犯两次同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错误？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是指亲自毁灭国家 杀害众人的错误吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我必须弥补自己犯下的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在只是 为了这个目的而活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那为什么那时你又不肯自爆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无法让13年来一直协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有如我女儿一般的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与我一同送死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉 是因为有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太狡猾了 竟然说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样叫我怎么朝你开枪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后一颗子弹 我会用在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将从你那里得来的性命还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要糟蹋自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想想自己该做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人不能只靠憎恨而活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:53.70,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:24:02.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:07.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:12.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:21.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:31.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:40.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:44.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.27,0:24:48.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:58.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你为什么要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 我们去找大家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.83,0:25:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.93,0:25:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,门的另一边…是海
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是水耶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.24,0:25:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这边 还有那边都是水
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.01,0:25:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.45,0:25:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『小小漂流者』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.82,0:25:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
